1.0.3.name: lmr/duo_auth
1.0.3.description: Duo Security two-factor authentication for Roundcube. Users have multiple ways to authenticate, including:  1. One-tap authentication using Duo’s mobile app. 2. One-time passcodes generated by Duo’s mobile app (works even with no cell coverage) 3. One-time passcodes delivered to any SMS-enabled phone. 4. Phone callback to any phone (mobile or landline!) 5. One-time passcodes generated by an OATH-compliant hardware token
